Manage Users

Manage users menu gives access to:

  1. The list with all users available in the system
  2. Options to deactivate and activate users
  3. Create new users

 

To deactivate a user use Deactivate action. The user becomes inactive and have no access to the system any more.

To activate inactive user use Activate action. The user becomes active and can login in the system.

To crate new user use Create user button.

For the user enter:

  • user id
  • First name
  • Last name
  • E-mail

The new user will receive a confirmation e-mail on the entered e-mail in the form.
